original: Jyllman, Axel Vilhelm, läroverksadjunkt, Jönköping, f. 3/8/92 i Jön-köp. — Stud:ex. i Jönköp. 11, fil. mag. i Upps. 18, provår i Lund 28. Vik. adj., e. o. ämneslär. v. Landskr. fo’lksk:sem. 19, i Trollhättan 19-20 o. 21-24, Tryde 20-21, Klippan 24, Ludvika 25-28, v. Jönköp. h. a. 1. 29-32, adj. i kemi o. biol. m. hälsolära där sed. 33. Skr.: Dvalin under 50 år (42).
translated: Jyllman, Axel Vilhelm, high school teacher, Jönköping, b. 3/8/92 in Jönköping. — Passed high school exam in Jönköping in 1911, BA in Uppsala in 1918, teaching practice in Lund in 1928. Temporary teacher, assistant teacher at Landskr. folk high school in 1919, in Trollhättan in 1919-20 and 1921-24, Tryde 1920-21, Klippan 1924, Ludvika 1925-28, vice principal in Jönköping from 1929-32 and chemistry and biology teacher with health education there since 1933. Written work: Dvalin under 50 år (1942).
